# Bata Takbo - Cloudflare Pages Reverse Proxy (Rewrites)
# Bypasses CORS and enables secure session cookies by proxying requests to your EC2 API.
# Replace https://api.yourdomain.com with your actual EC2 domain or public IP (e.g., https://your-ec2-ip)

/auth/* https://batatakbo-api.duckdns.org/auth/:splat 200
/admin/* https://batatakbo-api.duckdns.org/admin/:splat 200
/leaderboard/* https://batatakbo-api.duckdns.org/leaderboard/:splat 200
/api/* https://batatakbo-api.duckdns.org/api/:splat 200
/health https://batatakbo-api.duckdns.org/health 200
